T3 PMDM. Mapas

****https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/shapes

buscar tb events, setOnMapClickListener xa pinchar y poner en el mapa

Polygon --> addPolyline
.showInfoWindow --> muestra el bocadillo al picar
.hideInfoWindow --> oculta el bocadillo al picar
.moveCamera(CameraUpdateFactory.newLatLongZoom(newYor,15)) --> mueve el mapa a medida q picas

.setIcon(BipMap) --> cambiar icono del marker

****https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/examples/polyline-simple

